<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify Your RSOLV Setup</title>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap');

      body {
        font-family: 'Space Grotesk', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      .logo {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .logo img {
        max-width: 200px;
      }
      h1, h2, h3 {
        color: #10b981;
      }
      .checklist {
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .checklist-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .checklist-item input[type="checkbox"] {
        margin-right: 10px;
      }
      .status-box {
        background-color: #fff3cd;
        border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .success-box {
        background-color: #d4edda;
        border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .code {
        background-color: #2d3748;
        color: #e2e8f0;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        overflow-x: auto;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .cta {
        background-color: #10b981;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        display: inline-block;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6b7280;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        padding-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="https://rsolv.dev/images/rsolv_logo_transparent.png" alt="RSOLV Logo" />
      </div>

      <h1>Let's Verify Your RSOLV Setup</h1>

      <p>Hi {@first_name},</p>

      <p>
        It's been a few days since you signed up for RSOLV. We want to make sure you're all set up and ready to benefit from automated security scanning and remediation!
      </p>

      <div class="checklist">
        <h3>Quick Setup Checklist:</h3>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <input type="checkbox" disabled /> Connected your repositories for security scanning
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <input type="checkbox" disabled /> Added the GitHub Action workflow for automated fixes
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <input type="checkbox" disabled /> Set up your RSOLV_API_KEY as a repository secret
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <input type="checkbox" disabled /> Reviewed security issues found by RSOLV
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <input type="checkbox" disabled /> Generated and merged your first security fix PR
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Need Help with Setup?</h2>

      <p>If you haven't completed setup yet, here's a quick reminder of the steps:</p>

      <div class="code">
        # In .github/workflows/rsolv.yml:
        name: RSOLV Security Fixes

        on:
        issues:
        types: [labeled]

        jobs:
        security-fix:
        if: contains(github.event.issue.labels.*.name, 'rsolv:automate')
        runs-on: ubuntu-latest
        steps:
        - uses: rsolv-dev/rsolv-action@v1
        with:
        github-token: ${"{{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}"} rsolv-api-key: ${"{{ secrets.RSOLV_API_KEY }}"}
      </div>

      <div class="status-box">
        <strong>üéÅ Remember:</strong>
        Your first 10 fixes are completely free! No credit card required. After that, you only pay $15 per fix that gets deployed.
      </div>

      <h2>Common Questions We Get:</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Where do I get my API key?</strong>
          Check your welcome email or visit
          <a href="https://rsolv.dev/dashboard">your dashboard</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Can I use RSOLV on private repos?</strong>
          Yes! RSOLV works with both public and private repositories
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>What vulnerabilities does RSOLV detect?</strong>
          SQL injection, XSS, authentication flaws, hardcoded secrets, and 170+ other patterns
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>How secure is it?</strong>
          Every fix is analyzed for security impact and includes tests to verify the vulnerability is resolved
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="success-box">
        <strong>üí° Pro Tip:</strong>
        After RSOLV scans your repository and creates security issues, start with a HIGH severity vulnerability. Tag it with "rsolv:automate" to see how RSOLV generates secure, well-tested fixes.
      </div>

      <p>
        Ready to secure your code? Review the security issues RSOLV found, then tag any issue with "rsolv:automate" to generate a fix!
      </p>

      <a href="https://rsolv.dev/docs/getting-started" class="cta">View Setup Guide</a>

      <p>
        If you're stuck or have questions, just reply to this email. We're here to help you succeed!
      </p>

      <p>Best regards,<br />The RSOLV Team</p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          This email was sent to {@email}. If you no longer wish to receive these emails, you can <a href="{@unsubscribe_url}">unsubscribe</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          &copy; 2025 RSOLV - Proactive Security Scanning & Automated Remediation. Pay Only for Fixes You Deploy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
